oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Country Music Hall of Fame 25th Anniversary - Part 3
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 3 of 3. Recording is of a number of performances for the Country Music Hall of Fame 25th Anniversary. Segment is hosted by Ricky Skaggs (performer) and features: the Chieftains (performance group) and the Nashville Bluegrass Band (performance group). Recording occurred April 01, 1992.
